node.text:
I don’t want to shatter, Harpae 🦢🪞✨ Happy 5th anniversary to my favorite game Pocket Mirror 🦋🦢💖 Took this opportunity to draw my favorite character from the game, Harpae 💕💗 Who’s your favorite character if you know the game 🤔? Inspired by Harpae’s Theater 🎭 I swear there is always new details I notice every time I look back at this game 👀

I made some new brushes to try to replicate the watercolor texture style ☁️ I think I really love the result so I’m going to continue trying ✨ What do you think? It’s a tedious process but I enjoy trying something new 🌸

#digitalart #procreate #illustration #digitalpainting #watercolor #watercolorpainting

node.text:
Had a struggle on figuring out when to tell myself that this was a finish painting because I keep wanting to fix some details 🤧 How do you stop yourself working on the same piece for so long 😅 These problems makes me wonder if I forgot how to art 🙈✨

Update in my life, if you follow me on my YouTube vlogs or saw my Instagram story, you will know I just moved to Portugal 🇵🇹☺️☁️ I’m nervous about leaving the US and learning to live in a new culture but also excited 😊 Let me know if you have any recommendations to go to!! Just wanted to share that info 😄✨
